Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:33.08,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}許せば進めるし　恨みは立ち止らす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:38.08,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれは僕のせいにしな　それも僕のせいにしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:43.20,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君をずっと立ち止める　その全てと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:48.92,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕以外を許して　進んで行きなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:58.36,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生涯枯れることのない花　と名付けても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:03.47,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生涯枯れることのない花　になることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:08.58,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&HDA7B00&}真面目に生きていれば　いつか報われる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:13.62,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうやって言い切ってしまえば　それは嘘になる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:18.69,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}身に起こるその数十％　自業自得でも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:23.60,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}残りの数％　誰のせいでもないその不平等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:33.68,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H1200FF&\t(2560,2810,\3c&H265CF5&)\t(3269,3519,\3c&HDA7B00&)\t(3603,3811,\3c&H47C73E&)\t(3937,4103,\3c&H5F2558&)\t(4437,4562,\3c&H386A2D&)\t(5396,5438,\3c&H1200FF&)\t(6189,6481,\3c&H45B6FE&,\bord0.8)\t(8274,8441,\blur0,\3c&H103568&,\bord2,\1c&HCCE1F4&)\t(8775,9275,\3c&H52164B&)\t(9359,9609,\blur3,\3c&H103568&)}一番いけないことはさ　自分はダメだと思うこと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:38.68,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれは僕のせいにしな　それも僕のせいにしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:43.72,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕以外を許して進んで行きなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:49.29,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君自身のことも許してあげてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:33.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宽恕促人前行 仇恨让人停滞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:38.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那个当成我的错吧 把这个也归咎于我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:43.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原谅让你一直停滞不前之事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:48.92,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原谅除我以外的所有人 前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:58.36,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即便取名为永不凋谢之花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:03.47,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也无法永不凋谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:08.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&HDA7B00&}认真活着就会有回报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:13.62,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如此断言的话语必定是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:18.69,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百分之几十是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:23.60,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剩下的百分之几不怨任何人 如此不公
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:33.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H1200FF&\t(2560,2810,\3c&H265CF5&)\t(3269,3519,\3c&HDA7B00&)\t(3603,3811,\3c&H47C73E&)\t(3937,4103,\3c&H5F2558&)\t(4437,4562,\3c&H386A2D&)\t(5396,5438,\3c&H1200FF&)\t(6189,6481,\3c&H45B6FE&,\bord0.8)\t(8274,8441,\blur0,\3c&H103568&,\bord2,\1c&HCCE1F4&)\t(8775,9275,\3c&H52164B&)\t(9359,9609,\blur3,\3c&H103568&)}最糟糕的 是自我否定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:38.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那个当成我的错吧 把这个也归咎于我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:43.72,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原谅除我以外的所有人 前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:49.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也原谅你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:37.08,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうじゃない　求めるものは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:41.63,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}強くコノ手デ掴もう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:54.27,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}泣いたって変わらないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:23:00.94,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戻っても同じ　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:07.57,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大事なものが守れないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:14.54,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弱い僕のせい　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:20.25,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうして今　ここに僕がいる理由は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:27.30,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰が分からなくてもいい　そう　君がいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:34.06,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見境なく燃える炎を　雲中が指を指す
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:40.69,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕はきっと　強くなって　誰だって守り抜く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:48.78,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&}愛したい人の思い　闇をコノ手デ祓おう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:37.08,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是这样 我追求的是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:41.63,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亲手去紧握
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:54.27,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一味哭泣 则无法改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:23:00.94,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回到原点也一样 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:07.57,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无法保护珍视之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:14.54,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因为我太弱小 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:20.25,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么 我会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:27.30,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无人知晓也无妨 只要有你在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:34.06,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃尽万物的烈焰 直冲云霄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:40.69,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定要变强 保护所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:48.78,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1}心怀所爱之人 亲手驱散黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:50.78,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.22,0:00:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}降魔剑居然是明陀宗的本尊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父亲还和明陀有过接触
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快点接着念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我开始有种不好的预感了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然不知道胜吕的老爸想让我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.44,0:00:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雪男 总之你先继续念信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这里就是明陀宗以前的据点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.62,0:00:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}降魔堂就在这里面 我们抓紧时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是 那里真的安全吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.47,0:00:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这座不动峯寺以降魔堂为中心 就是为了守护它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}右眼原来应该是封印在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}物归原处才是上策吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好久没爬过这座山了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}七 八 九 十
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等等 你们这些猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她来了 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能接近这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在这里呀 蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你父亲很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.13,0:01:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}宝生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这里就是降魔堂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.59,0:01:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这里只有座主能进入 是不可侵犯的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我做了这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家一定不会原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是现在座主和本尊都不在了 这里只剩一个空壳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.23,0:02:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}护摩坛竟然还生着火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这里肯定有暗道 找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在证明住持大人 胜吕达摩能够信任之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:59.01,biaoti,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fax-0.15\fad(0,1022)\3c&HC4732D&\bord1.5\pos(356,605)}绵里藏针
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}降魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被奉为明王陀罗尼宗的本尊 代代相传的魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又名俱利伽罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相传 明陀始祖不角用此剑召唤了火之恶魔伽楼罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}用它的火之力打倒了不净王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从那以来 明陀宗代代将此剑奉为本尊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了封印残留的右眼 让它远离俗世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}定下了严格的戒律
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}像是在嘲讽这一切一般 他出现在了我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 你在说什么 那把剑是明陀的本尊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真啰嗦 我知道 秃驴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}反正这里头也是空的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在说些什么莫名其妙的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}八百造
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别碰我们的本尊 你个贼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}打倒他了吗 八百造
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真不愧是八百造
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他早就受了重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伤得这么重 亏他还能动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这人怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}达摩大人 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正十字骑士团日本支部 上一级驱魔师 藤本狮郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}金刚深山不动峯寺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你突然倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也不能就那样把你丢着不管 就把你搬到寺庙里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把我丢在那儿不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真是个老好人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能借个火吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比起这种事 藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}关于本尊 关于俱利伽罗 你知道多少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你为什么想要俱利伽罗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我怎么知道 上级叫我来的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大概是要用它杀小孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杀小孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他居然满不在乎地说出这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}身体能动了你就快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不管你有什么原因 我可不照顾一个杀小孩的恶人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我会走的 等我拿到降魔剑之后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你还不放弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你都不知道它在这不动峯寺的何处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要把每间屋子都找一遍不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 没那么多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还是问你更快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 剑在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这 这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是什么 想用它和我打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:06:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那里是… 不能去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}闭嘴 别胡闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}混蛋 你知道你在做什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是不和佛祖对话 佛祖就会放弃我们 我们就会失去力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我问你 只是祈祷就能救这些人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}披着圣人外衣的胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我最讨厌你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经不是做这种事的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必须尽快将瘴气的毒素排出体外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他 他们还能得救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能 他们所有人都能得救 大概
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去准备白萝卜 葱 缬草 菖蒲 岩盐 还有朝天椒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有凡士林 蜂蜡 猪油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们真的有救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:08:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要我说几遍啊 你去准备大量的热水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}点烟的火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果他真的 真的救了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虎子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}达摩 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虎子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}达摩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真的以为自己要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真的能生下这孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太好了 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢谢你 藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你来抢剑的时候 我还以为你是什么山贼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我误会你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:09:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这和那是两码事 把剑交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你看 我救了那么多病人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还教了你们治疗的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}给我点回礼也是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}达摩？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虎 虎子你先休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还以为你是好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真是我最讨厌的类型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不问你了 我自己去找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}害怕被玷污是无法前进的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唵 婀蜜哩帝 吽 癹吒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他逃了 快追
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能让那贼人活着走出这座山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爸 你在做什么啊 他可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}达摩 别以为这次我会轻易饶了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么正十字骑士团的驱魔师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不仅让邪教之徒进入了寺院 还让他去蛊惑人心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爸 他是我们的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他救了大家 救了虎子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这种事怎样都好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}知道了降魔剑和明陀秘密的外人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只能斩尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我有责任守护明陀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你守护的只是戒律吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我和你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}达摩 你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}达摩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别让他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可恶 真缠人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}害得我伤口都裂开了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}达摩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}降魔剑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:11:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我告诉你逃走的路线 跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你想干什么 这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没事 其实我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我小时候偷偷把剑拔出来过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想看一看伽楼罗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}结果伽楼罗和火焰都没有出现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那把剑只是个空壳 我一直都知道 却…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不想再膜拜一把空壳剑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我终于也下定决心 决定去战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我可是要用它去杀小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 你一定不会杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真是个无可救药的滥好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}脚印往那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你快逃 这样我们就两清了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样我们就和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可恶 他跳下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他在下面 我们绕过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:12:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}藤本和我的故事就到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}几个月之后 青之夜就发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父亲将座主之位以及明陀真正的秘密传给我 然后去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个秘密真的十分可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}藏在这里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们下去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没想到降魔堂里竟然有这样的地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把右眼给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但 但拿着两个会很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就快到了 而且我更担心你的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我有点后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只因为我的推测 就将我重要的学生卷进了这么不得了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想想你的今后 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:12:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你后悔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在能保护大家的只有我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我们打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是不净王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}安政五年 你们的祖先不角
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曾与附有火之恶魔伽楼罗的魔剑「俱利伽罗」结下契约
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们虽拼尽全力与不净王战斗 却未能将其斩杀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只能取其双目 将不净王封印
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在那之后 伽楼罗离开了俱利伽罗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是明陀宗传说的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是你们明陀宗代代守护的最深的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个是不净王？ 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这150年间一直在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那右眼和左眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:14:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是说 只要将右眼和左眼还给干涸的不净王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就能让不净王完全复活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}藤堂老师 你到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}宝生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是我重要的学生 虽然我也不忍心说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但你已经没有用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住持大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮 已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我会带你回到你父亲那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是会危害人类的毒瘤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必须在我这一代将其消灭 决不能留到下一代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由我来保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.47,0:14:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住持大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有碍此决意者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我明陀宗第十七代座主胜吕达摩决不饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:14:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在那青色的火焰中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我继承了明陀宗座主之位 知道了所有秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.90,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爸 你能听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:04.68,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爸 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别死啊 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吾名为伽楼罗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}乃明王陀罗尼座主之使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}汝乃先祖不角之子孙否
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}向吾示以血缘之证
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我 我是胜吕达摩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是不角的子孙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}确有不角之血缘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕达摩 吾今后将听命于汝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道代代座主都可以使役伽楼罗吗 这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}需要什么作为交换
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吾之所求乃秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吾之存在 吾为何听命于汝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一切真相皆为秘密 须死守
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是代价吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:16:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吾实则生于秘密 以谎言与猜忌之尘芥为食
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}作为交换 吾将予汝封敌之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}敌人是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不净王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沉睡于此佛堂地下余150年之残骸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伽楼罗啊 就是现在 给我力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住持大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}契约就是如此 我会答应你的所有请求
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伽楼罗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又叫朱雀或者不死鸟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是个不错的使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可恶的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然不知道你有何企图
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我绝不会让你轻易复活不净王的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放下右眼和左眼 退散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我这几年就是为了这个瞬间而活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伽楼罗焰 火食之印
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:16:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}身体能力好强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被恶魔附体之人大都如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.97,0:17:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伽楼罗焰 火粉之印
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恢 恢复速度跟不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是伽楼罗的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么就让我使出绝招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮 坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抓紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不净王要复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.15,0:17:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}降魔堂 他来这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住持大人 蝮也在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:17:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是柔造啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔造 小心那些飞沫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔造 你来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是八百造叫你来的吧 真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先不要管这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你能帮忙把蝮带到外派所 去叫增援吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个怪物到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但她把不净王的右眼放到身体里受了重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你替我将她带回她父亲那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那您呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我在这里阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住持大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要告诉大家真相 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住持大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们走 蝮 抱紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住持大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的秘密暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}与明陀宗座主的契约就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有和我个人定下的另一个契约吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在不净王开始成长并扩散瘴气之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}至少要使出净火封之印来拖住它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}使用净火封之印要消耗大量的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}使用劫波焰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}劫波焰是你为了打倒不净王而练
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}若是现在使用 你将永远失去打倒不净王的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有别的办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曩谟三满多母驮喃 阿钵囉底贺多 舍娑曩喃 哈诺迦诺迦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}佉佉 佉呬佉呬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}劫波焰 净火封之印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 暂时让它停住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:19:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这 这可真是费劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我都警告过你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还没死 只要活着就能找到打倒它的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我做了很对不住宝生同学的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为你太神秘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不会轻易出现在人前 也不知道你在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想了很久要怎样将你引出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.32,0:20:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只能想到复活不净王了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我早就知道明陀宗靠伽楼罗之力来封印不净王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但为了这一天 还是费了我好几年的工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的目标是你 胜吕达摩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 确切来说是你的使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}达摩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他把伽楼罗吃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他到底是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}超出想象的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}强行让伽楼罗附在了自己身上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}人类干涉恶魔 怎么会有这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.35,0:21:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.52,0:21:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}感觉年轻不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是伽楼罗的力量附带的好处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它在我肚子里乱窜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看来我这个容器还没法完全控制住它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过 总会适应的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.35,0:21:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样离我的目的又近了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢谢你了 胜吕达摩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}站 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:21:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拜托你了 奥村
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}希望你能用降魔剑打倒不净王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道这是个无理又勉强的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.02,0:22:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是如果 如果你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.46,0:22:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能像你父亲那样对我施以些许慈悲之心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.47,0:22:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想将希望寄托于你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.81,0:22:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢谢你看到最后 胜吕达摩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.54,0:24:05.38,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第七集 气焰万丈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.56,0:24:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥 把剑还回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.15,0:24:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他的火焰对到目前为止遇到的恶魔都有效
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.56,0:24:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}值得一试
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请打倒不净王
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.38,0:24:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}经三贤者以下的审问委员会投票决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.88,0:24:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}处决奥村燐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.10,0:24:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老头子 为什么要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.94,0:24:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
